<br>
I also stay aware of the fact that what comes around goes around. Clerics that are nice about giving a rezz and where the exchange between us goes well, is the sort I would remember down the road if I run into them again. If you were polite and friendly, then you would find me co-operative if you needed a corpse summon or some form of help a Necro can provide. <br>
<br>
If you were a rude little bitch then I'd skip out on a rezz and stop talking to ya, and dont bother me if you cant find yer corpse, yer problem...not mine.<br>
<br>
