<br>
Just yesterday, someone pulled a massive train of fiends to the zone.  From what I heard, it had been the 5th train in a half hour.  Busted the train, while young ones looked on, mouths hanging open.  Most had been on corpse runs.  Every corpse I saw between the Shadow Haven entrance and the bandit camps, I sent tells asking if they wanted a free 50% rez.  Most had expected to just make the run back without anything.  Normally, I don't expect payment for rezzes, nor do I accept them.  There have been many that have been generous with me on rezzes, so I figure I should pass on the generosity.  With working on tradeskills, the pp is nice, and I might even accept pp more as I rez more, but it is just mana, and said mana can always be gotten back.<br>
<br>
